	<div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/06/03/morning-agenda-frances-direct-appeal-on-bank/" data-title="Morning Agenda: France&#8217;s Direct Appeal on Bank" data-description="French officials are appealing to the United States on behalf of BNP Paribas. | Valeant&#039;s bid for Allergan raises a question about the role of drug companies. | Pilgrimâs Pride raises its bid for Hillshire Brands. | Trouble may be brewing at Salesforce.">
